{"id":101042,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/许宗衡买官送60斤现金，该“中央大员”是谁？/","date":"2010-08-27T17:13:37Z","modified":"2010-08-27T17:13:37Z","title":"许宗衡买官送60斤现金，该“中央大员”是谁？","content":"<p><p><span>香港《明报》报道，随着被开除党籍及公职，深圳前市长许宗衡的贪腐系列案件已进入司法程序，近日将在广西南宁开庭审理。京城消息透露，许宗衡所涉的一系列贪腐案，牵涉到深圳市内几乎所有领域的大型工程，涉案金额高达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多亿元人民币，而他以“金钱开路”的求官方式，是最终导致其仕途翻船的导火线。</span></p>\n<p><span>许宗衡是继郑少东、陈绍基及王华元之后，捲入黄光裕案的又一名副部级以上高官。消息称，由于许宗衡是湖南衡阳人，又长期在广东当官，故按照重大贪官异地关押审理的惯例，从他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月被中纪委“双规”起，就被拘禁在广西首府南宁市，案件亦由最高人民法院指定在南宁中级法院审理，而较早前广东省前政协主席陈绍基的贪腐案，就是在重庆市中 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idangxingdafa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}